sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant SPA as React SPA
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Service as Domain Service
    participant DB as Database

    User->>SPA: Submit workflow action
    SPA->>SPA: Validate form state
    SPA->>API: Send authenticated request
    API->>API: Validate token and schema
    API->>Service: Execute domain operation
    Service->>DB: Read or write records
    DB-->>Service: Return result
    Service-->>API: Return response model
    API-->>SPA: JSON response
    SPA-->>User: Refresh UI state
